This project includes modified components from realtime-whisper-webgpu by Xenova (Apache-2.0 licensed):

The following files have been used:

- src/App.jsx
- src/worker.js
- src/LanguageSelector.jsx
- src/Progress.jsx

Inside:

- src/renderer/src/containers/Captions.tsx
- src/renderer/src/workers/captionsWorker.ts
- src/renderer/src/components/WhisperLanguages.tsx
- src/renderer/src/components/Progress.tsx

Changes made:

- Rewritten to TypeScript
- Refactored state management
- UX overhaul including the removal of multiple components like AudioVisualizer and description
- Using system audio instead of microphone input

Original source: https://github.com/huggingface/transformers.js-examples/tree/main/realtime-whisper-webgpu

Modifications by Kote Kutalia, 2025